name: Ananth - Unedited Guitar Solo - 110126_2329.flac
description:
This is a raw, unprocessed, unedited recording of my guitar improvisation. I am in a highly experimental mode, guess it's evident from the work.

Of late, my ideas about creativity and music are undergoing big changes. This can be seen as an attempt to document my current mindset. In fact, it's the part of the search itself.

This song has many 'spots' that could give you a perfect musical experience. I may have left them understated or unpolished. I invite you all to use your imagination to fill the imperfections and enjoy the music. 

Gears used to Perform and Record this work:
Guitar: Yamaha Pacifica
Amp: Marshal MG-15CD
Mic: Shure SM-58
A/D: M-Audio Delta 1010 LT
DAW: Reaper
(1 track, 1 instrument (guitar), and one-shot recording. No tailoring. No Effects/Processing applied. Recording not 'rendered' from DAW to avoid any processing, but rather copied directly from where it keeps the recordings.)
